{"id":"07e879873ada5b3c997927f2fba5e43195c906bc586d218bc6bcb08a13f11871","item_id":"49571293bf:0","text":"Artists（艺术家）可以使用 Visualizer node（可视化节点）对 shading nodes（着色节点）和 material networks（材质网络）的部分进行 solo，以辅助 lookdev（外观开发）和艺术控制。"}
{"id":"a47fc931177cbfb4595d491897cd603035ee5041e1d4444b0f941551835b669f","item_id":"49571293bf:1","text":"这在调校 layer mask（层遮罩）的外观、调整 texture map（纹理贴图），或让玩具冰淇淋车上的 fingerprint grunge maps（指纹脏污贴图）看起来刚刚好时特别有用。"}
{"id":"f3d1f5871a9a8de7d75fc4dd7126e3286024cccbf4648f47107cb4357dbcc9ea","item_id":"49571293bf:2","text":"要 solo 某个节点或传入的 shading network（着色网络），只需选择想要 solo 的节点，然后按下"}
{"id":"e1b50f8378bc20e9e95a1ad1341464a1e2b23be09d5721141d77c319f7354734","item_id":"49571293bf:3","text":"键。"}
{"id":"d8c894d4097fbe4d3865176786e3cbfc6ba14d64edd5cd400392f8662d3ce2df","item_id":"49571293bf:4","text":"这样会插入一个 visualize 节点，并自动将所选节点的输出连接到"}
{"id":"66b8245886077eaaa79f378369261e020fb19d2c6ae53f94dfd8dfbc0282d029","item_id":"49571293bf:5","text":"visualize"}
{"id":"bb853680249ae0d0b2608016760e0147668a6db1229576b8b27fa4d5142d609f","item_id":"49571293bf:6","text":"节点的输入。"}
{"id":"bcb8b3203748ccac869d7195cb3d131c9964266b65291c6dc798057d420a321f","item_id":"49571293bf:7","text":"要对节点执行 “un-solo”（取消 solo），请断开输入到"}
{"id":"66b8245886077eaaa79f378369261e020fb19d2c6ae53f94dfd8dfbc0282d029","item_id":"49571293bf:8","text":"visualize"}
{"id":"80169edc21013fd5cb58deb3414059d76c8b642cbe599a0a864e4110ff29a658","item_id":"49571293bf:9","text":"节点的连接，然后继续进行 lookdev（外观开发）。"}
{"id":"88a9224b8559aa3aa99a96dd8dc0046695296fcdf74065c8bd4a5f2c77ac5c75","item_id":"49571293bf:10","text":"注意：由于 Solaris 内部的一些限制，某些用例中 visualizer 节点无法工作；但在大多数情况下，你仍然可以享受强大且富有创造性的 lookdev（外观开发）工作流。"}
